# home-assistant-openobserve (HACS only)

## Scope

- **This repo**: `custom_components/openobserve/` — HACS integration
- **Add-on repo**: https://github.com/Shaffer-Softworks/home-assistant-openobserve-addon (`openobserve_log_shipper/`)

## Integration

- Ingest: `POST /api/{org}/{stream}/_json` (JSON array)
- Default streams: `home_assistant_logs`, `home_assistant_events`
- Flush: 5s / batch 50
- Docker test URL: `http://openobserve:5080`
- Releases: workflow **Create release** → bump `manifest.json`, tag `v*`, asset `openobserve.zip`, PR to `main`

## Config flow

`OpenObserveOptionsFlowHandler` uses `self._config_entry` only (HA 2025.12+). No `super().__init__(config_entry)`.

## Deploy test

`./deploy/docker/run.sh` — does not include the Supervisor add-on.
